premise_source_doc_sentence: Joanne Rowling ,  (  -LSB- ˈrəʊlɪŋ -RSB- born 31 July 1965  )  , pen names J. K. Rowling and Robert Galbraith , is a British novelist , screenwriter and film producer best known as the author of the Harry Potter fantasy series .
